text: Daniyal Kenzhetayuly Akhmetov (; born 15 June 1954) is a Kazakh politician who was the 6th Prime Minister of Kazakhstan from 13 June 2003 to 9 January 2007.New Kazakh Prime Minister chosen Templeton Thorp == References == == Other websites == * Kapital.kz Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Kazakhstan
